data.description: Get ready to fall in love with this extra large 4  bedroom and 2 full bath cape cod with an oversized 2 car garage that sits on 1.41 acres with mature trees and a private park like setting.  This beautiful home has gorgeous hardwood floors,  new carpet, brand new windows throughout, new kitchen with 42" cabinets gorgeous granite countertops with newer all black appliances, kitchen overlooks the family room, all the bathrooms  plus the plumbing and electrical systems are all updated, wood stove in living room that can heat up the entire home for those extra cold winter nights.  You will probably find yourself sitting on the covered deck gazing at the extra large park-like backyard that has a ton of possibilities. The basement has  another family room that can be used as an additional bedroom and even more space to add additional rooms. You won't run out of places to store things with the large utility room and a separate room that would be great for additional storage. Upstairs you will find a separately metered one bedroom apartment WITH a washer and dryer that can be used as even more additional living space or live in one unit and rent the other. This will be a great start to your Airbnb journey!  This property is located in Baltimore county, just outside Woodstock and is close to just about everything including shopping, parks  695 & 70.  This wont last long, schedule your appointment today!
